<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>113</hymn_number>
<title>A KAN KHAMH CANG CH113</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 A kan khamh cang, khuaruahhar in, A kan Khamhbawi nih a thi cang;
 Rulhreu temnak a phoih dih cang. Bawi Jesuh nih a kan khamh cang.

[C1]
   A kan khamh cang, a kan khamh cang, A thlet thi in a kan tawl cang,
   Vailamtah cung thihnak a in; A kan Khamhbawi kei ca a thi.

[V2]
 A kan khamh cang, rulhreu temnak, A phoih dih cang keimah cungah; A
 kan Khamhbawi thangthat u si. A vailam kha pu cio u si.

[C2]
   A kan khamh cang, a kan khamh cang, A thlet thi in a kan tawl cang,
   Vailamtah cung thihnak a in; A kan Khamhbawi kei ca a thi.

[V3]
 Khamh a duh vial a khamh dih cang, Khuaruahharnak hlasa u si; Tingtang
 tum in thangthat u si. Khamhbawi min kha thangthat u si.

[C3]
   A kan khamh cang, a kan khamh cang, A thlet thi in a kan tawl cang,
   Vailamtah cung thihnak a in; A kan Khamhbawi kei ca a thi.</lyrics>
<key>Eb</key>
</song>